				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Concerned about High End raiding as a bard..<a name="40021"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 14 04 4:53 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Except Instruments, you wont see a difference DoT//Swarm Kiting mobs, who dont summon.
<br />

<br />
If You start kiting Summoning mobs, you might want to have more hp//ac.
<br />

<br />
Anyway you can solo more mobs, which cant be kited, like lets say as an example Shissar Assasin, (Vah Shir mask).
<br />
No place for kiting, no charms aviable --&gt; Must be meeled.
<br />
But you also can mezz//melee if ya dont got that ubbah equip.
<br />

<br />
Well, im not UBBAH equiped, but a way better than a bot 10aa bard.
<br />
It also will let ya tank mobs in HoH, Bot etc...
<br />

<br />
Im now drum maxxed for example, got all Instrument AAs, doing 182dmg with 1dot.
<br />

<br />
Instrumental Mastery gives 8dmg each lvl - = 4x8dmg = 32dmg.
<br />
With Karana Drum I was at 164 I guess... totally I do 50dmg more per dot, than a low AA bot bard...
<br />
Dunno if ModifierMaximizing AAs also do a difference.
<br />

<br />
But melee soloing... I got about 2,5-3k hp more than a bot bard, 
<br />
For Melee Soloing thats amazing ;)
<br />

<br />
You will also survive more AEs of mobs... Rampages... Pulling agro etc.
<br />
More time to hit Fading Memories...
<br />
More Mana for Fading, more for swarming...
<br />
Might survive a 50mob swarm hitting you ;)
<br />

<br />
Unkillable at duels :P
<br />

<br />
I like being &quot;stronger&quot; than some bards I see at PoV etc. <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />without being arrogant :P</span></td>
