				<td colspan="2"><span>Being a time equipped or better bard simply enables you to have a better chance to survive.  Whether it is from your own mistakes, other's mistakes, or really bad streaks of the RNG.
<br />

<br />
You'll have significantly more hitpoints/mana allowing you to &quot;tank&quot; and fade much better.  Also if you get lucky and are able to get the appropriate elemental+ items (War Drums, Abalone Mask or better, appropriate instrument mod items, etc.) you boost yourself in power and utility.</span></td>
